{"tid":732944,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦唔知點解開唔到機","createTime":"2018-07-07T10:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T12:59:04.000Z","uid":59473,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e9c5695a80a90dcb398f9ef800dbb7334a165b17","tid":732944,"uid":59473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T10:56:15.000Z","msg":"部電腦半年前係黃金砌完一直用都好地地<br />\n早一個月屋企跳完fuse部電腦就開唔到<br />\n(底板有著燈，係噤開機制0反應，風扇都無轉)<br />\n咁我就成部電腦枱出去整，去到用佢既電源線又可以開到機，所以就買過一條電源線。<br />\n返到屋企又真係開到機，如是姐用左兩個禮拜又開唔到機。<br />\n而岩岩又枱左部電腦出去整，點知又係去到個到又開到機，今次用埋我條電源線都開到。<br />\n以為屋企拖板問題，返到去換埋個新拖板都係開唔到機，叫埋樓下個電工師傅上黎check電路又話無問題。<br />\n<br />\n真係唔想再枱部電腦出去又得個吉，有無巴打有遇過類似既問題分享下點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f25ffe456330881b9d546cddb5507ced6f8978","tid":732944,"uid":59473,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"負評完又唔講野係咪知道發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9685f62734fdc39d55fd64fcf45ba6fbb1b32f68","tid":732944,"uid":59473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:41:49.000Z","msg":"虛心求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b8ed8ee7416129effe4906ddfb5403d5c2b6c7","tid":732944,"uid":66683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:43:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8bcf472bac634bcbb5ae5b3c85981c83e2eebf8","tid":732944,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:47:30.000Z","msg":"風水問題"},{"pid":"5fd6e04bb71ba8a81b2160b32bc5cb9ba602a703","tid":732944,"uid":59473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse